text: Österberg is a Swedish surname. Notable people with the name include: * James Osterberg, American singer, known professionally as Iggy Pop * Laura Österberg Kalmari (born 1979), Finnish football player * Martina Bergman-Österberg (1849–1915), Swedish-born physical education instructor * Mikael Österberg (born 1986), Swedish ice hockey defenceman * Sven-Erik Österberg (born 1955), Swedish politician ==See also== * Osterberg, German municipality * Østerberg, surname Category:Swedish-language surnames
